Output instructions:
- Add the IMAGE entry in rich content, as you have in the example, in node[0]
- Work on the "richContent" field to create multiple content blocks.
- make all article titles an H2, Bold with color #159B8B, follow the example.
- First paragraph doesn have an empty line before, it has an empty line after it, like the example.
- After a paragraph always add a line before the next H2, follow the example.
- give a space between the articles, follow the example.
- The conclusion should be a separate h2 with title "Our Take"
- Under message, add a parameter called "newsLetterSummary" with an html based exact same content. Do not apply any style, when using single quote, use the character "'".

